    ValueWithAttributes DateTimeStamp

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:DateTimeStamp

      • Description

        Time stamp of the creation.
        Additional Documentation 
        Type Value
        Implementers Assigned XSD Type: {http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}dateTime

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<DateTimeStamp create="2011-07-04T14:15:00+06:00" creatorID="c123456789" lastModifierID="m987654321" lastModify="2011-12-05T06:00:00Z" purge="2011-01-24" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4">2011-01-24T09:45:00-06:00</DateTimeStamp>

      Example JSON

      {
  "DateTimeStamp" : {
    "value" : "2011-01-24T09:45:00-06:00",
    "create" : "2011-07-04T14:15:00+06:00",
    "creatorID" : "c123456789",
    "lastModify" : "2011-12-05T06:00:00Z",
    "lastModifierID" : "m987654321",
    "purge" : "2011-01-24"
  }
}

      • Attribute Summary

        Attributes 
        Name Description
        create
        Time stamp of the creation.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:dateTime
        Example Value 2011-01-24T09:45:00-06:00
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        creatorID
        ID of creator. The creator could be a software system identifier or an identifier of an employee resposible for the creation.
        Details
        Type StringShort
        Example Value c123456789
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        lastModify
        Time stamp of last modification.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:dateTime
        Example Value 2011-01-24T09:45:00-06:00
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        lastModifierID
        Identifies the last software system or person to modify a record.
        Details
        Type StringShort
        Example Value m987654321
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        purge
        Date an item will be purged from a database (e.g., from a live database to an archive).
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:date
        Example Value 2011-01-24
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
